$OpenBSD: patch-etc_config_keycodes,v 1.2 2019/08/18 17:45:48 rsadowski Exp $

Fix keycodes for the "Left", "Down", "Up" and "Right" keys: they're
different between Linux and OpenBSD.

Index: etc/config.keycodes
--- etc/config.keycodes.orig
+++ etc/config.keycodes
@@ -38,13 +38,13 @@ bindsym XF86AudioMute exec --no-startup-id pactl set-s
